		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I rearranged the glyphs into mostly ASCII order, made a couple minor changes to <tt style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding:3px; background-color: #3355aa; color: white;">:;</tt> for consistency with other glyphs, and created a few missing glyphs <tt style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding:3px; background-color: #3355aa; color: white;">*+&lt;=&gt;@[]{|}~</tt>.

		
